comments: Teague (MIN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Porter Jr. (CLE) as he attempts to hand off the ball.
Thompson (CLE) and Martin (MIN) make marginal contact with each other during the pick.
Porter Jr. (CLE) seeks contact as he engages with Martin's (MIN) body during his shooting motion but contact does not affect his ability to maintain legal position during his jump shot attempt.
Thompson (CLE) slightly extends his hip against Teague's (MIN) body during the pick.
Garland (CLE) takes more than two steps after he has gathered the ball.
Vonleh (MIN) clamps Thompson's (CLE) arm during the rebound and restricts his ability to pursue the ball with two hands.
Vonleh (MIN) makes marginal contact to Thompson's (CLE) arm during his shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (CLE) makes marginal contact to Martin's (MIN) body after the release of his shot attempt as he contest the shot.
Thompson (CLE) slightly extends his body against Graham's (MIN) body during the pick.
Graham (MIN) connects with Sexton's (CLE) body during his drive that affects his SQBR.
Porter Jr. (CLE) briefly engages with Covington's (MIN) arm prior to the screen.
Vonleh (MIN) slightly extends his arm against Porter Jr. (CLE) body during the screen but contact is marginal.
Covington (MIN) slightly extends his arm against Porter Jr. (CLE) during the screen but contact does not prevent him to disengage from the play.
Thompson (CLE) jumps vertically as he defends Teague (MIN) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Covington (MIN) makes marginal contact to Sexton's (CLE) arm during the pass.
Okogie (MIN) commits a take foul on Porter Jr. (CLE).
Dellavedova (MIN) briefly engages with Covington (MIN) during the rebound but contact does not affect his ability to gather the loose ball.
Porter Jr. (CLE) makes contact to Teague's (MIN) body during his shooting motion that affects his drive shot attempt.
Covington (MIN) commits a take foul on Thompson (CLE).
Porter Jr. (CLE) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Teague (MIN) off ball.
Culver (MIN) commits a take foul on Sexton (CLE).
Sexton (CLE) makes marginal contact with Teague's (MIN) body during his drive to the basket.
Dellavedova (CLE) places a resting hand against Napier's (MIN) side during his shooting motion but quickly disengages during his driving shot attempt.
Covington (MIN) makes contact with Nance Jr.'s (CLE) arm as he gathers the rebound and contact affects his ability to retrieve the ball.
Nance Jr. (CLE) reaches across and makes contact to Covington's (MIN) arm on his shot attempt.
Covington (MIN) commits a take foul on Dellavedova (CLE).
